{{External|rs=Mature}}

'''Mature ales''' are [[members]]-only, stronger versions of regular [[ale]]. They provide stronger [[skill]] [[boosts]], larger deboosts, and heal more than the regular versions. These are '''only''' obtainable through [[brewing]], where there is a chance that a batch of ale matures during the brewing process. Leaving an ale in the [[fermenting vat]] after it has fully set will not turn it mature. The chance of brewing a mature ale increases from 5% to 36% by adding [[the stuff]] to the vat after adding in [[barley malt]].{{Refn|Testing has shown it is not 64% as Mod Ash was previously cited and likely closer to 36%. Please comment on [[Talk:Brewing]] with questions, comments, or if you want to contribute data.}} The stuff cannot be used to make [[mature cider]], the player must rely on the 5% chance. It is purchasable from [[Honest Jimmy]] for 50 [[pieces of eight]], a reward from the [[Trouble Brewing]] [[minigame]].

